en_982844_1	There is a high possibility for evening thundershowers over most parts of the island today Fairly heavy falls OF about 75 to 100 mm are likely at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central, North-western and Uva Provinces and in the Galle, Matara, Anuradhapura and Vavuniya Districts.
en_982844_2	Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Western, Sabaragamuwa, Central and North-central provinces during the morning.
en_982844_3	The public are called upon to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by temporary localized strong winds and lightning during thundershowers.
en_982844_4	The Met Department meanwhile said that showers or thundershowers will occur in the sea areas extending from Mannar to Matara via Colombo and Galle.
en_982844_5	Showers or thundershowers will occur at a few places over other sea areas in the evening or night.
en_982844_6	Winds will be South-easterly or variable in direction and speed will be 10 to 30 kmph in the sea areas around the island.
